What is WARP?

HyperElk is the best combat rotation bot available for World of Warcraft. We are proud to offer our service at a very competitve price with all the premium rotations for both retail and WOTlK included in your subscription.

We are constantly developing new features and updating our rotations to offer the best service available to our users.

Key Features

Security

No Injection, No Memory Hack, No LUA Unlock. Driver based and randomized inputs.

Premium Retail and WOTLK Rotations Included

Unlike many other WoW Combat Rotation Bots, HyperElk includes premium PvE Rotations for Retail and WOTLK as part of the base subscription. This type of Combat Rotation is typically hidden behind a paywall on other platforms.

Damager Dealer, Tank and Healer Supported

Get the best out of HyperElk regardless of your specialization. 

Free and Fast Updates

The rotations included and the software are updated after each game updates. No downtime on patch days!

Multilanguage Client Support

HyperElk works with the WOW client in any language and with most keyboard types. 

Stellar Support

Fast support from our Moose Support Team, Deer Dev’s and the community on Discord.

Powerful API

Create your own rotations with our powerful and well documented API.

Easy Setup

Autobind all the required keybinds automatically, get started within minutes.

Auto Updates

Cloud stored rotations ensures you always have the latest updates from our Devs.

User Friendly Interface

You can use both the external or in game GUI to control and monitor the behavior of HyperElk. 

Full Automation or Mixed Gameplay

HyperElk can automatically detects when cooldowns or aoe spells must be used. These features can also be disabled/custom to suit your gameplay.

Question & Answers

Do we support PVP?

PVP Rotations are not provided in the basic subscription.

We do, however, offer "Paid" PVP Rotations, which are part of our "Community Rotations" section, available to subscribers. Please be advised, that not all Classes/Specs are supported or offered, as it is up to the developers if they wish offer a PVP Version of their PVE Rotations.

We do offer a few guides and api support channel in Discord if you wish to create your own.

Do we support WoW Classic? (WOTLK / SOM)

Yes, we have Core Support for WoW Classic WOTLK and SOM.

However, only WOTLK has rotations provided by the developers. The full list of supported classes and specs can be found on Discord.

We do not provide any rotations for SOM.

Do we support private server?

We generally dont support private servers if they run a different version of wow.

This includes most wotlk servers. 

What payment type is supported?

We only offer payment via Stripe and there are no plans to support any other payment type.

Does we have a reseller?

No, we do not have a reseller and have no plans to allow for resellers.

How long have you been providing this software?

We have been public since 2020, before this, it was a private project between the Developers.

When was the last Ban wave?

We have not had a ban wave directly associated to using our product. We do our best to provide a safe solution to you and keep your account safe.

However, please be advised that no automation software is 100% safe and you should not use the software on an account you can't afford to lose.

Do we read memory?
We are a high performance "pixel software", we do not read any game memory or inject into the process. We are a stand alone software.
